snippet.title: Commodore 64 Longplay  - The Mask of the Sun
snippet.description: Full playthrough of the game The Mask of the Sun for Commodore 64 computers, developed by Ultrasoft and published in North America by BrÃ¸derbund and in Europe by Ariolasoft in 1982. The game is also available for Atari XL and Apple II. The graphics offers crude animations in some areas, making it different form other games form the epoch.
